videos.headline: Western Kentucky RB Wales goes 15 yards for the TD
videos.description: Western Kentucky RB Anthony Wales receives the handoff and runs 15 yards into the end zone for the score.

videos.headline: LA Tech ties game off 48-yard pick-six
videos.description: Louisiana Tech's L'Jarius Sneed picks off Western Kentucky's Mike White and returns the interception 48 yards for the touchdown to tie the game 10-10.

videos.headline: Wales dives for second rushing TD of game
videos.description: Western Kentucky RB Anthony Wales runs 26 yards before diving for the pylon to give the Hilltoppers the lead back over Louisiana Tech.

videos.headline: Ryan Higgins pass to Carlos Henderson for 6 yds for a TD
videos.description: Ryan Higgins pass complete to Carlos Henderson for 6 yds for a TD (Jonathan Barnes KICK)

videos.headline: Wales scores third TD of first quarter
videos.description: As time expires in the first quarter, Mike White throws a short touchdown pass to Anthony Wales for the running back's third touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Ryan Higgins pass to Jarred Craft for 5 yds for a TD
videos.description: Ryan Higgins pass complete to Jarred Craft for 5 yds for a TD (Jonathan Barnes KICK)

videos.headline: WKU WR Taylor hauls in 45-yard TD
videos.description: Western Kentucky QB Mike White throws just beyond two Louisiana Tech defenders to Taywan Taylor for a 45-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Mike White pass to Taywan Taylor for 4 yds for a TD
videos.description: Mike White pass complete to Taywan Taylor for 4 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Western Kentucky's Dennis Edwards ejected for targeting
videos.description: WESTRN KENTUCKY Penalty, Personal Foul (Dennis Edwards) to the LaTch 31

videos.headline: Ryan Higgins pass to Kam McKnight for 53 yds for a TD
videos.description: Ryan Higgins pass complete to Kam McKnight for 53 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Kam McKnight run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.description: Kam McKnight run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Anthony Wales breaks tackle for fourth overall TD
videos.description: Western Kentucky RB Anthony Wales receives a shovel pass, breaks a tackle and cruises into the end zone for a 15-yard touchdown, his second receiving score and fourth overall of the game.

videos.headline: LA Tech's Trent Taylor makes a great one-handed catch
videos.description: Louisiana Tech WR Trent Taylor makes an excellent one-handed catch for a first down early in the fourth quarter against Western Kentucky.

videos.headline: Anthony Wales goes untouched for fifth TD
videos.description: Western Kentucky RB Anthony Wales takes the handoff and cruises into the end zone untouched for a 13-yard touchdown, his third rushing score and fifth overall.
